Title: Prodigy
Plot: Carter must help keep a promising young cadet from throwing away a future at the SGC. O'Neill and Teal'c encounter a dangerous life form at an offworld research base.
Writer: Joseph Mallozzi, Paul Mullie, Brad Wright
GuestStars: Elisabeth Rosen, Michael Kopsa, Hrothgar Mathews, Keith Martin Gordey, Roger Haskett, Russell Farmer, Ivon R. Bartok, General Michael E. Ryan
